Class ClusterShardingSetup

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.pekko.actor.setup.Setup
      • org.apache.pekko.actor.typed.ExtensionSetup<ClusterSharding>
        • org.apache.pekko.cluster.sharding.typed.scaladsl.ClusterShardingSetup
  • public final class ClusterShardingSetup
extends ExtensionSetup<ClusterSharding>
    Can be used in pekko.actor.setup.ActorSystemSetup when starting the ActorSystem to replace the default implementation of the ClusterSharding extension. Intended for tests that need to replace extension with stub/mock implementations.
